                     MAyo, or Majo, has on the East and North-East Roscommon and Slego; 
                     Bounds. on the West the Main Western Ocean; on the North with the same Ocean; and on the South with the Country of Gallway. It is in length 58 Miles, and


in breadth 44. A fertile County, abundantly rich in Cattel, Deer, Hawks, and plenty of Honey.

